OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FTurning
OL,6,Fwetter to end Tuesday as outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain spread across the region. These
OL,8,Fcontinuing on-and-off overnight with
OL,9,Fdrier intervals. Becoming murky over
OL,10,Fthe mountains with cloud lowering and
OL,11,Fresulting in hill fog. Warm and muggy.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FWednesday starts grey and
OL,14,Fmisty with spells of rain. Low cloud
OL,15,Flifting with some warm spells of
OL,16,Fsunshine developing during the day,
OL,17,Fthough still a chance of an afternoon
OL,18,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
