OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FLikely remaining humid and unsettled
OL,7,Fon Thursday and Friday with outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain and low cloud. Potentially
OL,9,Ffresher and drier on Saturday with
OL,10,Fsome spells of warm sunshine.
